<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Words Containing GH</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Word of the Day · Bingo · English Solver</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">GH is one of English's trickiest digraphs — sometimes silent (NIGHT), sometimes an /f/ (COUGH), and sometimes a hard /g/ (GHOST). In Scrabble, this inconsistency is your advantage. G is worth 2 points and H is worth 4, giving GH a 6-point base that amplifies on premium squares.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Why GH Is Valuable in Scrabble</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
