    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">6 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">G(2) + H(4) base</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">300+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid GH words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Sound variations</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The H tile's 4-point value means every GH word starts strong. Words like GHASTLY (14 pts) and MIGHTY (14 pts) combine the digraph with common tiles for reliable high scores without needing rare letters.</p>

